This is a patch to TitanGraph's 0.4.4 code lucene index module to fix an issue with occasionally inconsistent search results from Lucene.

The patch branch from Titan is available here:
https://github.com/jsight/titan/tree/0.4.4_branch

The Titan Bug report is here:
https://github.com/thinkaurelius/titan/issues/656

Further information on how the issue affects Windup is availabe at the following JIRA:
https://issues.jboss.org/browse/WINDUP-75

